        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "Orginally a ghoul to support Bindusara's reserch in to faith based hunters, you proved worthy of the embrace. Keeping to your knowlage you started learning of Golcanda and the redemtion the Inncou promised. Sabatos brought you in to the sect and over the centuries you moved to the Americas. Learning that Sabatos was residing in Los Angeles, you started giving information back and forth, mostly dealing with the New Promise. The last message you recived from Sabatos was that the local ventrue were going to betray him, at the same time the Prince of Los Angeles Pictor was going to defect to the Inncou. This was 6 months ago, with out any other communcation you are worried about your old friend. Your ventrue contacts have told you where court is being held."
